  "detailed_description": "In this game you buy code to make programs. Instructions in those programs can move a little creature that collects more coins and code lines for you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665030/extras/a7a23c6151c2f364b9f3590006030fd0.poster.avif?t=1711981369\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665030/extras/a7a23c6151c2f364b9f3590006030fd0.webm?t=1711981369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665030/extras/a7a23c6151c2f364b9f3590006030fd0.mp4?t=1711981369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can use conditions and loops.<br></li><li>All maps you enter are generated randomly, so you get to play unique level every time.<br></li><li>Collect new commands on the game field.<br></li><li>You also have \"shoot\" command to destroy walls and kill the monsters.</li></ul>",
